

Give the notification a name and scroll down and tick the box next to EXECUTE PROGRAM. Under Program File, select Demo exe notification - outfile.ps1 from the drop-down. 
		Finally, in the parameter field, enter a command. For our purposes, we will add a new local admin user by entering test.txt;net user prtgadm1 Pwn3d_by_PRTG! /add;net localgroup administrators prtgadm1 /add. During an actual assessment, we may want to do something that does not change the system, such as getting a reverse shell or 
		connection to our favorite C2. Finally, click the Save button.
		
		
		After clicking Save, we will be redirected to the Notifications page and see our new notification named pwn in the list.


